      "id": "emoji",
      "package_type": "content-bundle",
      "version": "1.0.0",
      "display_name": "Emoji",
      "summary": "Optional common emoji font supplement and emoji picker input method for chat reactions.",
      "description": "Emoji installs an optional common-emoji content supplement font pack and a\nsmall emoji picker input method.\n\nIt is not a locale. It does not change translated UI text or the active\nlanguage. The font pack exists so received chat messages containing common\nreaction emoji can render instead of showing missing-glyph boxes. The IME pack\nexists so devices with the shared compose widget can insert the same basic\nreaction set.\n\nIncluded payload:\n- emoji-core: content-only LVGL binfont generated from Noto Emoji Monochrome\n  with a small reaction-focused charset.\n- emoji-picker: generic candidate picker backend with candidates stored in\n  pack payload.\n\nThis package is intentionally distributed as an Extensions download. It is not\npart of the default firmware image.",
      "author": "Trail Mate",
      "homepage": "https://vicliu624.github.io/trail-mate/",
      "min_firmware_version": "0.1.30-alpha",
